During the year the games we play in the playground change.Nearly all year round the boys play football.In September and October we play conkers When it snows we make snowmen and have snowball fights.In the spring and Summer we play Kingy,rounders,marbles, twosy ball,skipping and queen who's got the ball.We have rhymes for some of the games we play.
Queen who's got the ball {Queen,queen who's got the ball, {I haven't got it, {It isn't in my pocket.
Skipping Rhyme. {Cowboy Joe from Mexico. {Hands up,Stick em up, {Don't forget to pick em up, {Before you go. }
